Gabbana, who was previously in a relationship with Dolce, added, “Life has its natural course, there are things that must not be changed. And one of these is the family.”

Rich, neutral shimmers. Polished, shining metallics. Fun, inspiring jewel tones and brights. I am so impressed and happy with the range of colours, shades and finishes in this palette. Urban Decay put a lot of thought in to this palette and they did a fantastic job on it.
